					<dateRange>
						<fromDate standardDate="0306">306</fromDate>
						<toDate standardDate="0359">359</toDate>
					</dateRange>
					<descriptiveNote>
						<p>Born probably of Christian parents in the early years of the 4th cent. in the region of Nisibis, he spent most of his life in Nisibis, serving a series of bishops (beginning with Yaʿqub of Nisibis, d. 338).</p>
					</descriptiveNote>
